data.description: Welcome to 1202 Coastal Bay Blvd in Coastal Bay, a charming gated community near US1. This 3-story, 2-car garage townhome offers comfort and style. The 1st-floor room is versatile for your needs. The kitchen on the second level boasts 2023 stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook. The third floor features a tranquil primary suite with a walk-in closet and updated en-suite bathroom. Another bedroom has its own updated en-suite bathroom. Coastal Bay ensures security with entrances on 23rd St and Federal Highway. The HOA includes a pool, jacuzzi, fitness room, internet, and cable TV for a complete and convenient lifestyle. Welcome to 1202 Coastal Bay Blvd, situated in the desirable neighborhood of Coastal Bay, a charming gated community nestled near US1. This location will captivate you with its proximity to schools, parks, pristine beaches, downtown Delray, and much more. This delightful 3-story, 2-car garage townhome offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by marble flooring that spans throughout the home. The 1st-floor room presents a significant opportunity to tailor the space to best fit your needs. Heading to the second level, the well-appointed kitchen features 2023 stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast nook, creating a culinary haven for both daily meals and entertaining guests. On the third floor, the primary suite is a tranquil retreat, boasting a spacious layout, a walk-in closet, and an updated en-suite bathroom with elegant finishes. The additional bedroom has its own updated en-suite bathroom, providing flexibility for a growing family, a home office, or guest accommodations. Coastal Bay, a small gated community, ensures a sense of security, conveniently positioned with entrances on both 23rd St and Federal Highway. With an extremely reasonable HOA that includes a pool, jacuzzi, fitness room, internet, and cable TV, this residence offers a complete package for a comfortable and convenient lifestyle.
